1
00:00:43,060 --> 00:00:46,780
=Auspicious Nobles=

2
00:00:47,580 --> 00:00:49,940
=Episode 3=

3
00:00:49,940 --> 00:00:52,500
(The Crown Prince Takes What He Wants)

4
00:00:53,240 --> 00:00:54,960
I'm nothing more
than a carefree wanderer.

5
00:00:55,280 --> 00:00:56,840
I have no interest in court affairs.

6
00:01:01,710 --> 00:01:04,870
Tower Master, I hope you'll reconsider.

7
00:01:06,680 --> 00:01:07,480
There's no hurry.

8
00:01:09,920 --> 00:01:10,840
Take care.

9
00:01:26,120 --> 00:01:26,680
Tower Master.

10
00:01:26,950 --> 00:01:29,150
Your voice-changing skill is incredible.

11
00:01:29,150 --> 00:01:29,950
Naturally.

12
00:01:29,950 --> 00:01:32,480
I'm practically
an expert in voice acting.

13
00:01:33,510 --> 00:01:34,070
Caiyuan.

14
00:01:34,350 --> 00:01:36,000
Have Jiuzhu follow that creep.

15
00:01:36,010 --> 00:01:36,990
Keep him under constant watch.

16
00:01:37,310 --> 00:01:38,640
I turned him down just now.

17
00:01:38,660 --> 00:01:40,690
He's definitely figuring out
how to get back at me.

18
00:01:42,870 --> 00:01:44,200
Get Second Prince here at once.

19
00:01:44,430 --> 00:01:47,000
I need to teach him
some modern business principles.

20
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:48,200
Yes, Tower Master.

21
00:01:49,500 --> 00:01:51,020
(Wangshi Tower)
Yang.

22
00:01:51,040 --> 00:01:52,950
Will we get to see
the Tower Master today?

23
00:01:52,950 --> 00:01:54,430
What if we don't?

24
00:01:55,070 --> 00:01:56,400
The Tower Master of Wangshi Tower

25
00:01:56,400 --> 00:01:57,680
holds power beyond measure.

26
00:01:58,600 --> 00:02:00,290
Even the Crown Prince
and the Second Prince

27
00:02:00,310 --> 00:02:02,040
rely on her support.

28
00:02:02,200 --> 00:02:04,390
Even if she has us beaten,
we'll have no one to complain to.

29
00:02:06,040 --> 00:02:08,840
I don't even know
how I offended the Tower Master.

30
00:02:09,150 --> 00:02:11,000
If I can't earn her forgiveness today,

31
00:02:11,470 --> 00:02:12,910
I'm afraid my life will be at risk.

32
00:02:13,310 --> 00:02:15,280
How could we have
offended the Tower Master?

33
00:02:15,750 --> 00:02:17,310
Who's trying to set us up?

34
00:02:17,310 --> 00:02:17,840
I don't know.

35
00:02:18,080 --> 00:02:18,750
Tower Master.

36
00:02:18,960 --> 00:02:21,080
The Helilao Restaurant
you told me to open

37
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:22,680
is making nearly 7,000 taels a month.

38
00:02:23,150 --> 00:02:24,520
(Zheng Yuanzhao, Great Yong's Second Prince)
It's already the most popular restaurant in the capital.

39
00:02:24,530 --> 00:02:25,790
Tables are fully booked every day.

40
00:02:27,140 --> 00:02:27,940
(Account Book)

41
00:02:28,710 --> 00:02:31,400
(It costs 30,000 taels a day
just to keep the restaurant running.)

42
00:02:31,680 --> 00:02:34,590
(A few thousand taels
barely scratches the surface.)

43
00:02:35,030 --> 00:02:35,800
Tell me.

44
00:02:36,360 --> 00:02:37,310
Why haven't you met

45
00:02:37,310 --> 00:02:38,500
the performance target I set?

46
00:02:40,150 --> 00:02:42,030
The restaurant is doing well,

47
00:02:42,240 --> 00:02:44,470
but making 100,000 taels
a month is nearly impossible.

48
00:02:44,840 --> 00:02:46,240
For the sake of everything I've done

49
00:02:46,240 --> 00:02:47,870
for the Li family over the years,

50
00:02:48,080 --> 00:02:49,090
You don't have to anymore.

51
00:02:55,080 --> 00:02:56,280
But with Helilao,

52
00:02:56,560 --> 00:02:58,190
you take most of the profits.

53
00:02:58,430 --> 00:02:59,680
I only get twenty percent.

54
00:03:00,360 --> 00:03:01,840
And you're still pushing me this hard.

55
00:03:02,280 --> 00:03:03,400
That's just not fair.

56
00:03:03,680 --> 00:03:05,470
If you can't do it, just say so.

57
00:03:05,630 --> 00:03:07,840
I can always train someone else.

58
00:03:08,710 --> 00:03:10,630
Tower Master, don't forget.

59
00:03:11,190 --> 00:03:14,190
I, Zheng Yuanzhao,
control the empire's merchant network.

60
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:15,560
I'd say I'm the only one

61
00:03:15,560 --> 00:03:17,870
in all of Great Yong who can meet

62
00:03:17,870 --> 00:03:18,890
that... what do you call it?

63
00:03:19,590 --> 00:03:20,560
That performance target.

64
00:03:21,360 --> 00:03:21,800
Besides,

65
00:03:22,630 --> 00:03:23,870
even if you replaced me,

66
00:03:24,400 --> 00:03:26,030
you'd never find anyone as obedient

67
00:03:26,430 --> 00:03:27,870
or as easy on the eyes.

68
00:03:31,280 --> 00:03:31,750
Fine.

69
00:03:32,280 --> 00:03:33,590
Then let's revise your target.

70
00:03:34,030 --> 00:03:35,280
You're lowering it?

71
00:03:36,590 --> 00:03:38,470
10,000 taels a day.

72
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:39,400
This...

73
00:03:40,190 --> 00:03:40,960
How much?

74
00:03:41,750 --> 00:03:42,750
10,000 taels.

75
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:46,400
Tower Master,

76
00:03:46,560 --> 00:03:48,000
why don't you see how much I'm worth

77
00:03:48,280 --> 00:03:49,150
and just sell me?

78
00:03:50,180 --> 00:03:51,280
There's no way I can do it.

79
00:03:52,190 --> 00:03:53,840
I know you can't.

80
00:03:54,430 --> 00:03:55,560
But what if I told you

81
00:03:56,080 --> 00:03:57,800
I could make
every merchant in the empire

82
00:03:57,960 --> 00:03:59,280
earn money for us?

83
00:04:06,870 --> 00:04:09,470
Every merchant in the empire
working for us?

84
00:04:10,080 --> 00:04:11,000
In a few days,

85
00:04:11,360 --> 00:04:13,840
I'll give you the perfect plan.

86
00:04:14,360 --> 00:04:15,520
All you need to do

87
00:04:15,910 --> 00:04:17,430
is build the platform

88
00:04:17,430 --> 00:04:18,480
and expand the business.

89
00:04:19,270 --> 00:04:20,870
Now you've really made me curious.

90
00:04:21,510 --> 00:04:23,070
Who are you, Tower Master?

91
00:04:24,190 --> 00:04:26,390
Could you truly be
an immortal sent from heaven?

92
00:04:27,630 --> 00:04:28,560
If only I could

93
00:04:28,800 --> 00:04:31,160
catch a glimpse
of the Tower Master's true face today.

94
00:04:31,240 --> 00:04:32,040
Mind your manners!

95
00:04:33,390 --> 00:04:34,390
Break his legs.

96
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:34,830
Yes.

97
00:04:35,040 --> 00:04:35,480
Guards.

98
00:04:35,480 --> 00:04:35,920
Hold on.

99
00:04:36,240 --> 00:04:37,680
Since the Tower Master is too shy

100
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:39,430
to reveal her true face today,

101
00:04:40,240 --> 00:04:42,360
I'll come back another time.

102
00:04:42,720 --> 00:04:43,480
Another time.

103
00:04:45,720 --> 00:04:46,800
(Wangshi Tower)
My dear, she's out.

104
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:47,950
She's out.

105
00:04:50,190 --> 00:04:51,480
Please let the Tower Master know

106
00:04:51,480 --> 00:04:54,190
that my husband is the General
of the Northern Expedition Cavalry.

107
00:04:54,200 --> 00:04:55,680
He wishes to request
an audience with the Tower Master.

108
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:56,480
Never heard of him.

109
00:04:56,800 --> 00:04:58,120
Do you have an appointment letter?

110
00:04:58,920 --> 00:05:00,480
An appointment letter?

111
00:05:00,920 --> 00:05:01,830
No.

112
00:05:01,920 --> 00:05:03,800
If that's required,
I'll write one right away.

113
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:04,600
Do you think

114
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:07,160
just anyone can enter Wangshi Tower?

115
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:08,920
Even those who qualify

116
00:05:09,040 --> 00:05:11,310
must submit an appointment letter
seven days in advance.

117
00:05:11,550 --> 00:05:13,040
Only after the Tower Master reviews it

118
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:14,480
will she decide whether to see you.

119
00:05:17,270 --> 00:05:19,480
Hey, may I ask
which family you belong to?

120
00:05:19,480 --> 00:05:21,220
How did you manage
to meet the Tower Master?

121
00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:22,830
Mind your own business.

122
00:05:22,920 --> 00:05:23,600
Move along.

123
00:05:25,300 --> 00:05:27,120
I... I'm a General
of the Northern Expedition Cavalry.

124
00:05:27,510 --> 00:05:29,830
If you can arrange
a meeting with the Tower Master,

125
00:05:29,830 --> 00:05:31,360
I'll reward you handsomely.

126
00:05:31,370 --> 00:05:32,990
A General
of the Northern Expedition Cavalry?

127
00:05:33,530 --> 00:05:34,800
You really think you're somebody.

128
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:38,160
Who does he think he is?

129
00:05:39,160 --> 00:05:39,750
Your Highness.

130
00:05:42,360 --> 00:05:44,270
No wonder that fool Yuanzhao

131
00:05:45,190 --> 00:05:46,480
managed to double

132
00:05:46,480 --> 00:05:48,510
the imperial merchant business
in just a year.

133
00:05:49,390 --> 00:05:51,070
So Wangshi Tower has been backing him.

134
00:05:51,110 --> 00:05:53,300
His Majesty has always used
the Second Prince to keep you in check.

135
00:05:53,310 --> 00:05:54,750
If the Second Prince
and Wangshi Tower...

136
00:05:54,750 --> 00:05:56,000
I know.

137
00:05:58,040 --> 00:06:00,070
Since Wangshi Tower
insists on helping Yuanzhao,

138
00:06:02,070 --> 00:06:03,360
then make her disappear.

139
00:06:03,360 --> 00:06:03,870
Yes.

140
00:06:14,660 --> 00:06:18,780
(Jiuzhu, Great Yong's top assassin.
The Tower Master's personal shadow guard)

141
00:06:26,190 --> 00:06:27,190
What a headache.

142
00:06:31,870 --> 00:06:33,360
The imperial merchant business

143
00:06:33,430 --> 00:06:36,000
brings in 70,000 taels a month.

144
00:06:37,750 --> 00:06:38,750
I'm ashamed.

145
00:06:39,310 --> 00:06:40,950
I've been tied up with too many affairs

146
00:06:40,950 --> 00:06:42,040
and neglected the business.

147
00:06:42,060 --> 00:06:43,710
That's why the profits are a little low.

148
00:06:43,750 --> 00:06:45,160
Please punish me, Father.

149
00:06:46,510 --> 00:06:47,480
You little rascal.

150
00:06:48,390 --> 00:06:49,920
You say you're ashamed,

151
00:06:49,920 --> 00:06:51,790
but you're really
waiting for me to praise you.

152
00:06:52,120 --> 00:06:54,070
You think you can fool me

153
00:06:54,480 --> 00:06:56,920
(The Emperor of Great Yong)
with that little act of playing humble?

154
00:06:57,700 --> 00:06:58,920
You're wise as always, Father.

155
00:06:59,160 --> 00:07:00,630
No one knows me better than you.

156
00:07:02,430 --> 00:07:03,270
You

157
00:07:03,720 --> 00:07:04,920
are capable and intelligent,

158
00:07:04,920 --> 00:07:06,420
yet never arrogant
because of your achievements.

159
00:07:07,040 --> 00:07:09,120
Unlike Yuanhe, who's
so stubborn and headstrong.

160
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:16,310
It's just a pity
you were born a few years too late.

161
00:07:17,430 --> 00:07:18,310
Otherwise...

162
00:07:20,950 --> 00:07:23,270
Starting tomorrow,
join me at morning court.

163
00:07:24,070 --> 00:07:25,270
It's time you learned

164
00:07:25,270 --> 00:07:26,720
how to handle affairs of state.

165
00:07:27,240 --> 00:07:28,830
No, Father.

166
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:31,310
I'm perfectly happy
making a little money every day

167
00:07:31,720 --> 00:07:33,920
and living as a carefree rich man.

168
00:07:37,070 --> 00:07:37,800
Very well.

169
00:07:38,270 --> 00:07:40,270
Since your ambitions lie elsewhere,

170
00:07:40,310 --> 00:07:41,920
I won't force you.

171
00:07:42,830 --> 00:07:43,680
Your Majesty.

172
00:07:43,830 --> 00:07:45,600
The Crown Prince has arrived.

173
00:07:46,720 --> 00:07:47,360
Father,

174
00:07:47,360 --> 00:07:49,430
I've already
finished reporting the accounts.

175
00:07:49,430 --> 00:07:50,350
I'll take my leave now.

176
00:07:51,310 --> 00:07:52,120
Zhao.

177
00:07:52,720 --> 00:07:54,830
You've handled
the imperial merchant business well.

178
00:07:55,270 --> 00:07:56,510
I'm very pleased.

179
00:07:59,750 --> 00:08:01,800
Greetings, Father.

180
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:04,510
Yuanhe.

181
00:08:04,920 --> 00:08:06,000
The Inspectorate again.

182
00:08:06,270 --> 00:08:07,160
Take a look.

183
00:08:07,510 --> 00:08:09,920
These are all memorials impeaching you.

184
00:08:10,240 --> 00:08:12,510
As long as I can rid Great Yong
of its corrupt officials,

185
00:08:12,720 --> 00:08:15,240
why should I fear impeachment?

186
00:08:15,300 --> 00:08:16,360
Still as stubborn as ever.

187
00:08:16,830 --> 00:08:19,560
A single move in the imperial court
can affect the whole kingdom.

188
00:08:19,560 --> 00:08:21,390
(That cold, arrogant face again.)

189
00:08:21,390 --> 00:08:23,180
(No wonder nobody
likes him wherever he goes.)

190
00:08:23,360 --> 00:08:26,070
(My warm smile is much more charming.)

191
00:08:26,070 --> 00:08:27,500
The court is losing people's support.

192
00:08:30,720 --> 00:08:31,360
Your Highness.

193
00:08:31,800 --> 00:08:34,240
I'll get the list
of every official who impeached you

194
00:08:34,520 --> 00:08:36,290
and have
the Inspectorate investigate them.

195
00:08:36,300 --> 00:08:38,150
Let's see if any of them
are truly above reproach.

196
00:08:38,150 --> 00:08:38,910
There's no need.

197
00:08:40,120 --> 00:08:41,440
They're nothing more

198
00:08:41,720 --> 00:08:43,360
than the Second Prince's pawns.

199
00:08:43,750 --> 00:08:45,270
They pose no threat to me.

200
00:08:46,240 --> 00:08:48,000
But that Tower Master of Wangshi Tower

201
00:08:48,120 --> 00:08:50,240
sure has been going all out
to help Yuanzhao.

202
00:08:53,770 --> 00:08:54,840
Why did you ask me to come?

203
00:08:56,080 --> 00:08:57,080
What took you so long?

204
00:08:58,760 --> 00:09:00,240
I've been trying to reach you all day.

205
00:09:00,510 --> 00:09:02,630
Didn't I already tell you?

206
00:09:02,910 --> 00:09:04,870
A professional errand runner

207
00:09:05,120 --> 00:09:06,360
is all about speed.

208
00:09:06,750 --> 00:09:08,440
The moment your client calls,

209
00:09:08,600 --> 00:09:09,720
you've got to get here fast.

210
00:09:10,240 --> 00:09:12,440
So much for Great Yong's top assassin.

211
00:09:14,150 --> 00:09:15,510
I've lost that little gadget.

212
00:09:16,360 --> 00:09:17,200
I can't hear you.

213
00:09:18,080 --> 00:09:18,550
You...

214
00:09:19,150 --> 00:09:19,630
This...

215
00:09:19,840 --> 00:09:21,480
This won't do.

216
00:09:21,840 --> 00:09:23,320
How am I supposed to reach you

217
00:09:23,320 --> 00:09:24,460
the next time I'm in trouble?

218
00:09:25,910 --> 00:09:28,150
It cost me a fortune

219
00:09:28,510 --> 00:09:30,550
to make it with ultrasonic bianstone.

220
00:09:30,550 --> 00:09:32,480
Besides, it goes pretty well

221
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:38,150
with your outfit.

222
00:09:45,120 --> 00:09:46,750
How's the surveillance

223
00:09:47,030 --> 00:09:48,150
on the Crown Prince going?

224
00:09:53,000 --> 00:09:54,240
I've learned my lesson.

225
00:09:54,670 --> 00:09:56,510
Business comes after payment.

226
00:09:58,670 --> 00:09:59,440
Ten taels.

227
00:10:01,210 --> 00:10:04,080
The Crown Prince watched the Second Prince
after he left Wangshi Tower.

228
00:10:04,370 --> 00:10:06,450
I'm guessing that after the attack
on the Li Residence,

229
00:10:06,480 --> 00:10:09,080
he suspects you've already joined forces

230
00:10:09,080 --> 00:10:10,360
with the Second Prince.

231
00:10:11,030 --> 00:10:12,720
I was having too much fun back then.

232
00:10:12,730 --> 00:10:13,960
That never even crossed my mind.

233
00:10:18,390 --> 00:10:18,960
This is bad.

234
00:10:19,190 --> 00:10:20,480
That scheming prince must think

235
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:22,260
we're plotting a rebellion
with the Second Prince.

236
00:10:22,960 --> 00:10:23,440
Caiyuan.

237
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:24,440
Pass the order.

238
00:10:24,670 --> 00:10:25,750
Abandon this hideout.

239
00:10:26,510 --> 00:10:28,480
Seal off the entrance
at Yinma Town as well.

240
00:10:28,520 --> 00:10:29,960
Suspend production
at the workshop for one month.

241
00:10:29,960 --> 00:10:30,790
Tower Master,

242
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:33,120
that's a lot of money to lose.

243
00:10:33,120 --> 00:10:34,440
We're already short on funds.

244
00:10:34,520 --> 00:10:37,190
Even if the Crown Prince knows
the Second Prince is connected to us,

245
00:10:37,200 --> 00:10:38,630
do we really
have to shut everything down?

246
00:10:38,630 --> 00:10:40,510
I know we can't afford to.

247
00:10:40,510 --> 00:10:42,630
This will cost us millions of taels.

248
00:10:43,120 --> 00:10:44,790
But the Crown Prince is a madman.

249
00:10:44,900 --> 00:10:46,720
He's bound to think
we're helping the Second Prince

250
00:10:46,720 --> 00:10:47,960
take his throne.

251
00:10:47,960 --> 00:10:50,200
If we stay, we'll all be dead.

252
00:10:50,630 --> 00:10:53,240
You dared meddle
in the affairs of the imperial family.

253
00:10:53,960 --> 00:10:55,720
And now you think you can run?

254
00:10:57,510 --> 00:10:58,670
Too late.

255
00:11:00,440 --> 00:11:01,000
Hurry!

256
00:11:02,670 --> 00:11:03,480
Hurry!

257
00:11:03,510 --> 00:11:04,080
Tower Master,

258
00:11:04,150 --> 00:11:05,960
why is the street completely empty?

259
00:11:06,100 --> 00:11:06,910
Don't worry about it.

260
00:11:07,030 --> 00:11:08,360
We're racing against death now.

261
00:11:08,360 --> 00:11:10,850
One step too slow, and that lunatic
might catch up and kill us.

262
00:11:14,440 --> 00:11:17,200
I really do jinx myself.

263
00:11:17,200 --> 00:11:18,630
What do we do, Tower Master?

264
00:11:18,870 --> 00:11:20,240
Just stay calm. Act natural.

265
00:11:20,240 --> 00:11:20,720
Okay.

266
00:11:24,910 --> 00:11:25,480
Keep moving.

267
00:11:29,200 --> 00:11:31,550
My Lady, don't worry.

268
00:11:31,750 --> 00:11:33,630
With the Tower Master's guidance,

269
00:11:34,120 --> 00:11:37,030
the young master's business
has come back to life.

270
00:11:53,910 --> 00:11:54,720
Stop right there!

271
00:12:01,200 --> 00:12:04,590
♪Snowflakes settle gently
upon your brows♪

272
00:12:05,350 --> 00:12:08,730
♪Your dark hair
brushes across my fingertips♪

273
00:12:09,500 --> 00:12:11,240
♪Your smile♪

274
00:12:11,500 --> 00:12:13,790
♪Melts away the winter snow♪

275
00:12:13,790 --> 00:12:17,470
♪One fleeting glance says more
than a thousand words♪

276
00:12:17,930 --> 00:12:21,240
♪Yet I stand before you♪

277
00:12:21,980 --> 00:12:25,810
♪Unable to recognize your eyes♪

278
00:12:26,230 --> 00:12:28,150
♪Though fate tries♪

279
00:12:28,150 --> 00:12:30,730
♪To make us pass each other by♪

280
00:12:30,950 --> 00:12:34,370
♪I choose to make our story whole♪

281
00:12:34,630 --> 00:12:36,260
♪Though time slips by♪

282
00:12:36,260 --> 00:12:38,020
♪As day turns into night♪

283
00:12:38,540 --> 00:12:42,560
♪I still remember
our days at Wangshi Tower♪

284
00:12:42,980 --> 00:12:45,360
♪One glance at you lasts a lifetime♪

285
00:12:45,360 --> 00:12:47,150
♪Blessed by fate♪

286
00:12:47,150 --> 00:12:52,310
♪I believe this moment
will last forever♪

287
00:12:52,310 --> 00:12:54,750
♪Your smiling face♪

288
00:12:54,750 --> 00:12:57,590
♪Is the most beautiful poem♪

289
00:12:57,590 --> 00:13:01,210
♪I'd rather spend my days with you♪

290
00:13:01,730 --> 00:13:05,190
♪And wander the world together♪

291
00:13:05,190 --> 00:13:06,530
♪Holding you close♪

292
00:13:06,530 --> 00:13:09,070
♪Envying neither lovers nor immortals♪

293
00:13:09,070 --> 00:13:11,390
♪Your tenderness♪

294
00:13:11,390 --> 00:13:14,250
♪Is the brightest moon♪

295
00:13:14,250 --> 00:13:17,950
♪I'd rather
pledge three lifetimes to you♪

296
00:13:18,470 --> 00:13:21,760
♪Our love will never fade away♪

297
00:13:21,760 --> 00:13:24,220
♪Though heaven and earth grow old♪

298
00:13:24,750 --> 00:13:29,000
♪My heart will remain forever pure♪

